"""
Minimal Pattern Studio
--------------------------------------------------------
Workflow:
1) Choose a template (preview shows slot layout)
2) Upload motifs (individually or as a sheet, auto-detected)
3) App places them automatically per template (position, size, rotation fixed)
4) Optional: swap assignment (which motif goes in which slot)
5) Download als scharfes, transparentes PNG

Run locally:
    pip install streamlit pillow numpy scipy
    streamlit run pattern_tool.py
"""

